"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai has played a crucial role in the South African Men's Hockey team, according toGood Things Guy.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kraai\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"a crucial role\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"the South African Men's Hockey team\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"Things Guy\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team secured their Olympic qualification by defeating Egypt 2-1 in the final last November.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9931742170664092, \"rank\": 0.006865052425364581, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic qualification\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the final last November\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More recently, they beat Pakistan 4-3 in the bronze medal playoff at the FIH Nations Cup in Poland.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999912498752493, \"rank\": 8.749032130234627e-06, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pakistan\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal playoff\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the FIH Nations Cup\", \"from\": 1152, \"t