bpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kraai\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"both his province\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"various levels\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zenani Kraai emphasised the importance of accessible community sports programmes.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2025, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zenani\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"accessible community sports programmes\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is especially important in areas like Langa where they are more available compared to other townships.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"areas\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"other townships\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These programmes showed me that success was possible in my situation,\\\" he noted.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These programmes\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"my situation\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai's journey has not been easy.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kraai's journey\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in Langa, he faced social and economic challenges.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social and economic challenges\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He missed birthdays, milestones, and family occasions to train and attend national team camps.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"birthdays\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"milestones\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"family occasions\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"national team camps\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During difficult times, he leaned on his family and coach for support.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"difficult times\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Am I ever going to make it where I see myself?\\\"\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he often wondered.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But their encouragement kept him going.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their encouragement\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His self-resilience also played a key role.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His self-resilience\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"a key role\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Things will not stay like this, someday it will change,\\\" he would remind himself.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Things\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He believed that hard work would eventually pay off.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not cheat yourself.\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Put in the hours and the selections and results will reflect your hard work.\\\"\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hours\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"the selections\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"your hard work\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Kraai, success is not just about personal achievements.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kraai\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2978}, {\"ngram\": \"personal achievements\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can inspire others through the way I have walked, or to walk a better path\\u2026 not the achievements but to be an example to those who look like and have lived a life like mine, then I have found success,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [], \"no